UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1577
1 (c) Upon conclusion of the evidence, the court shall instruct the jury on the
2 range of punishment, and counsel for the defendant may present arguments
3 followed by counsel for the Commonwealth. The jury shall then retire and
4 recommend a sentence for the defendant.
5 (4) If the jury reports to the judge that it is unable to agree as to the sentence or any
6 portion of the sentence, the judge shall impose the sentence pursuant to KRS
7 532.090.
